01_001_001.Text: This is how God created the universe: In the beginning God created the earth.

Token.Text: This is how God created the universe: In the beginning God created the earth.

01_001_002.Text: But at that time she was deserted, and there was only water on it. There was no light all around. God's Spirit hovered over that water.
